Master Program: Software Engineering of Distributed Systems
Thesis: Opinion Mining in Social Media

~~~ Twitter Crawler ~~~
Crawl all tweets, a specific region or specific keywords
Create a crawler.cfg file for specifying application and database details

usage: twitterCrawler.py [-h] [--location [LOCATION [LOCATION ...]]]
                         [--track [TRACK [TRACK ...]]] [--db DB]

Twitter Crawler

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --location [LOCATION [LOCATION ...]]
                        Getting stream of tweets according to location:
                        <southwestLongitude> <southwestLatitude>
                        <northeastLongitude> <northeastLatitude>
  --track [TRACK [TRACK ...]]
                        Getting stream of tweets tracking the keywords:
                        <word1> <word2> ...
  --db DB               Choose the name of collection for database Twitter.
                        Default: tweets

